article.description: — Trey Pulliam had 15 points as San Diego State beat Saint Mary's 63-53 on Friday night at the Jerry Colangelo Classic.
article.headline: San Diego St. tops Saint Mary's (Calif.) 63-53
article.linkText: San Diego St. tops Saint Mary's (Calif.) 63-53
article.story: PHOENIX -- — Trey Pulliam had 15 points as San Diego State beat Saint Mary's 63-53 on Friday night at the Jerry Colangelo Classic. Matt Bradley had 14 points for San Diego State (7-3). Adam Seiko added 12 points. Tommy Kuhse had 13 points for the Gaels (10-3). Matthias Tass added 12 points and three blocks. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
